    algebraMap (MvPolynomial Œπ K) (FractionRing (MvPolynomial Œπ K)) r := by
  rcases IsLocalization.surj  (nonZeroDivisors (MvPolynomial Œπ K)) p with ‚ü®‚ü®u, v, hv‚ü©, huv‚ü©
  simp only at huv
  rcases gcd_dvd_left u v with ‚ü®r, hr‚ü©
  rcases gcd_dvd_right u v with ‚ü®s, hs‚ü©
  use r, s
  have gcd0 : gcd u v ‚â† 0 := by
    simp
    rintro rfl rfl
    simp at hv
  refine ‚ü®?_, ?_, ?_‚ü©
  ¬∑ rintro rfl
    simp at hs
    subst v
    simp at hv
  ¬∑ intro x hxr hxs
    rcases hxr with ‚ü®r, rfl‚ü©
    rcases hxs with ‚ü®s, rfl‚ü©
